Register variables and makes them available globally in the shields.

[[e]]
echo "### Methods\n";
foreach (glob(PAGE . DS . $url->path . DS . '*.page') as $v) {
    if (basename($v, '.page') === basename(dirname($v))) continue;
    $v = Page::open($v);
    echo "\n - [" . $v->title . '](' . $v->url . ')';
}
[[/e]]

Here are list of variables that are available globally in the shields:

 - `$config`
 - `$date`
 - `$language`
 - `$site`
 - `$state`
 - `$url`
